<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Leeway Rides | Business & Referral Partnerships</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --primary-purple: #1b022b; --secondary-purple: #2a0845; --accent-gold: #f3ad21; --light-gold: #ffcf68; --gold-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3ad21 0%, #ffcf68 50%, #c48206 100%); --text-light: #ffffff; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--primary-purple); color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.6; }
        h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
        .top-bar { background: #11011c; padding: 8px 5%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.9rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(243, 173, 33, 0.3); }
        .top-bar a { color: var(--accent-gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        header { background: rgba(27, 2, 43, 0.95); padding: 15px 5%; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .logo-img { height: 40px; width: auto; }
        nav ul { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 20px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        nav a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--accent-gold); }
        .btn-gold { background: var(--gold-gradient); color: var(--primary-purple); padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; border: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; }
        .content-section { padding: 60px 5%; max-width: 900px; margin: auto; }
        .content-section h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; color: var(--accent-gold); margin-bottom: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; }
        .content-section p { margin-bottom: 20px; color: #ddd; }
        ul.styled-list { margin: 20px 0 30px 20px; color: #ddd; }
        ul.styled-list li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .lead-form-box { background: var(--secondary-purple); border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .lead-form-box h3 { color: var(--light-gold); margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
        .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .form-group.full-width { grid-column: span 2; }
        .form-group label { margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--light-gold); }
        .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea { padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid rgba(243, 173, 33, 0.4); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        footer { background: #09000f; padding: 40px 5% 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; }
        .copyright { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { header { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; } .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .form-group.full-width { grid-column: span 1; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <div><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Corporate & Institutional Transportation Partnerships</div>
        <div>Call/Text: <a href="sms:+19803923216">980-392-3216</a></div>
    </div>
    <header>
        <a href="index.html">
            <img src="7689.png" alt="Leeway Rides Logo" class="logo-img">
        </a>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="airport.html">Airport</a></li>
                <li><a href="medical.html">Medical</a></li>
                <li><a href="local.html">Local</a></li>
                <li><a href="areas.html">Service Areas</a></li>
                <li><a href="partners.html">Partnerships</a></li>
                <li><a href="contact.html">Contact & Book</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-gold">Request Ride</a>
    </header>
    <main class="content-section">
        <h1>Business & Referral Partnerships</h1>
        <p>Leeway Rides collaborates with organizations, facilities, and corporations that require dependable, professional transportation solutions for clients, members, patients, residents, or employees.</p>
        
        <h3 style="color: var(--light-gold); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Potential Partners Include:</h3>
        <ul class="styled-list">
            <li>Hospitals, medical offices, oncology centers, and dialysis facilities</li>
            <li>Rehabilitation facilities, assisted-living communities, and senior living centers</li>
            <li>Adult day programs, home-care agencies, and group homes</li>
            <li>Case-management organizations and behavioral-health providers</li>
            <li>Churches, community organizations, and nonprofits</li>
            <li>Employers, hotels, and corporate travel coordinators</li>
            <li>Schools, training programs, and local institutions</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Need dependable transportation for your clients, patients, residents, or employees? Contact Leeway Rides to discuss a customized transportation partnership.</p>

        <div class="lead-form-box">
            <h3>Partnership Inquiry Form</h3>
            <form action="mailto:Leewayridesnow@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="form-grid">
                <input type="hidden" name="Source" value="Partnership Page Inquiry">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Organization Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" name="OrgName" required placeholder="Organization Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Contact Person *</label>
                    <input type="text" name="ContactPerson" required placeholder="Full Name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Job Title</label>
                    <input type="text" name="JobTitle" placeholder="Title / Role">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Phone Number *</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="Phone" required placeholder="980-392-3216">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Email Address *</label>
                    <input type="email" name="Email" required placeholder="example@organization.com">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Type of Organization</label>
                    <input type="text" name="OrgType" placeholder="Medical, Senior Living, Corporate...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Estimated Trip Frequency</label>
                    <input type="text" name="Frequency" placeholder="Daily, Weekly, As needed...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Service Area / Location</label>
                    <input type="text" name="ServiceArea" placeholder="Shelby, Charlotte, Gastonia...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Number of Passengers Typically Transported</label>
                    <input type="text" name="PassengerVolume" placeholder="Approximate volume">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Desired Start Date</label>
                    <input type="text" name="StartDate" placeholder="Timeline">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <label>Is Invoicing / Corporate Billing Needed?</label>
                    <select name="InvoicingNeeded">
                        <option value="Yes">Yes, require monthly or periodic invoicing</option>
                        <option value="No">No / Flexible</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <label>Additional Partnership Details</label>
                    <textarea name="Notes" rows="3" placeholder="Share specific requirements or scope..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group full-width">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-gold" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px;">Submit Partnership Inquiry</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="copyright">&copy; 2026 Leeway Rides / LTS Connect Network. All Rights Reserved.</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
